Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米克里欧  莱菈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这三天来都在发高烧很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为史雷成为我的宿主而造成的影响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是艾莉莎帮了你那真不知如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了！  艾莉莎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  你终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么有食欲的话看来已经不用担心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎一直在照看我吧  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该说谢谢的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你拔出湖中少女的圣剑的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出色地平息了那场祭奠中的骚乱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中从未如此兴奋过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.74,0:01:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而在那里我所想到的话就是「谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.45,0:01:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀着这份感谢的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件东西请你务必收下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:20.44,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1300,1300)\pos(258,568)\blur2}导师的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师的装扮很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很合身呢史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人靠衣装嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羡慕就直说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那里有天族在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫米克里欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这里的是莱菈  被大家称为湖中少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是注定要成为导师的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们即使离天族这么近也毫无办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她听不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  请试着握住艾莉莎的手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着通过史雷将我们的声音传达给艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得见吗  艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莱菈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎没听见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么史雷  请把眼睛闭上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎  听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是史雷的注意力不够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  好好闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次把鼻子捏上  呼吸也停住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了  女性的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是米克里欧大人的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天族的米克里欧大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我至今的无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有觉得那是无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎  我们天族看得见你们的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请绝对不要轻视天族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的心灵会产生污秽  招致灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的感谢确实传达给我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有别的好办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷作为导师能变得更强的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就不需要再像这样屏蔽知觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说我更努力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就都能听见天族的声音了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎是原本就有天赋才能听见的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是连我也能交谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了天族是的的确确和我们在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得很兴奋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎大人  差不多到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:06:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我接下来得去一趟王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  我们也一起去城里看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师出现的传闻不断扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民众们就自发地竖起了旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民众们心里也是盼望着导师出现的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  听了艾莉莎的话感觉有点紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷竟然也会紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你送我  艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意  那么待会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才开始就想吐  感觉很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说身体好了是骗人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上是真的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到了城里就渐渐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  那是因为污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,污秽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像还混杂着别的污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从哪里传来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法知道得那么清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的史雷的话应该是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请试着集中注意来感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷的身体没问题的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的莱菈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不适感还没消除  但没开始那么严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道为什么遗迹会产生污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能把躲在府上的导师交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你们？  你是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在我们的管辖之下才是明智的吧  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这是评议会的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会把导师交给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是门不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却哪都找不到钥匙孔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这就是——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封印的门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是推测
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了不让人看到这里面的东西而藏起来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印的话应该有作为解除封印的钥匙的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩对遗迹都很熟悉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候说到玩耍都是和米克里欧去遗迹探险的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海兰德王家的纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:10:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记还给艾莉莎了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是靠这个也许就可以解除封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫因祸得福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的污秽非同寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:58.07,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(696,652)}Doragon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳  是「龙」的石像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾难的化身  毁灭的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被视为不祥的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是竟然做出这种东西放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座遗迹果然有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,污秽的量也远比别处多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座雕像就是这里的污秽的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外在什么地方还有散发着污秽的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭魔！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝙蝠？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭魔化的蝙蝠聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米克里欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗米克里欧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样没完没了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  能再一次让凭魔分散开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的火焰一下子全部净化掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾火起舞  红莲业岚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.14,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(619,652)}Tornado  Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风火焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了莱菈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  身体没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和我的契约  史雷的负担比以前更重了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想尽量减轻负担的时候我会到里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时请说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗  这就是「到里面去」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后还会和其他的天族缔结契约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这会成为史雷的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但请不要忘记这也是有代价的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以身体难受的时候我就到里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座遗迹的污秽没有因此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错  污秽的原因在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座遗迹的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是生前对抗权贵  被不为人知地埋葬的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眷念和怨恨变为强烈的污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使肉体毁灭了也仍然像残渣一样在这里积累
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至产生了凭魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法对民众说明的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上存在这样的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎对这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈是想给我看这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师应该平息的是孕育凭魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可称为污秽的源泉的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「灾祸的显主」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾祸的显主…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放出异常的污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时甚至能改变世界形态的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是灾祸的显主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平息那个家伙才是导师真正的使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道的还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这样即使遇到了灾祸的显主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会被他的污秽所吞没吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望你能得到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让史雷后悔的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被使命所束缚  周游世界  增长见识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之后带着得出的答案去面对灾祸的显主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用考虑得太复杂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说周游世界的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  是水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,污秽竟然已经如此渗透在瑞迪雷克中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在这里太危险了  史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了  天花板…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是大地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被污秽侵蚀的大地感到很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  米克里欧  莱菈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是污秽造成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个说是污秽也太过于巨大…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷！  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那不懂变通的性格也是很顽固呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是你的廉洁将瑞迪雷克往好的方向引导
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此  巴尔托洛他们的目的不是想得到导师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的目的是要将我从王政中排除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然明白那我也没什么说的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是巴尔托洛也做了什么手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说马林顿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样我也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马林顿正遭受疫病折磨也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说必须得有人去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要做我所能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太背包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是非常担心你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强的风啊  但愿不会出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周休息！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.29,0:22:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想悠闲地泡温泉来消除疲劳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  米克里欧  让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:22:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈  那就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:22:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前得给大家做预告才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:22:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预告？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热情传说X的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.35,0:23:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  我们听说下周休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.27,0:23:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈知道下周是什么故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蒙混过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始感到不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷  这样下去不能再出场了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真消极呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是让你用这一周来想象并期待下周的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱菈再不快点就丢下你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周「灾难的开始」  敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会出场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:06.42,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}向着遥远前方的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.72,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}你顺风而行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:16.60,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}追寻的答案不易找到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:20.97,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}从开始就已明白才跨出的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:30.47,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}梦想的足迹  无数次绕远路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:34.97,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}将描绘好的世界地图展开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.48,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}回响吧！风之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:43.66,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}闭上眼睛  心中的声音鼓舞着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:49.04,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}目的地还在更高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:52.04,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}传递吧！风之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:57.15,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}侧耳倾听  心中的声音满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:03:02.37,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}释放出耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:06.14,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}你化为蓝色的旋律吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:18.78,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}此刻闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:26.69,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在这不归的旅途上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:32.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在片刻的安宁中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:39.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}我们怀着愿望入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:46.63,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}梦中的世界被光明照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:53.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}满溢的热情  寄宿着希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.07,0:22:01.80,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}为了明天暂作休憩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:07.57,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}我们现在在这里欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:13.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}它将在这旅途的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:20.53,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}一定会抓住命运的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:26.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在此时此处描绘着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:31.50,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:38.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}共同前行
